### Hadith 3:732

*Narrated Abu Huraira:*

The Prophet said, "When your servant brings your meals to you then if he
does not let him sit and share the meals, then he should at least give
him a mouthful or two mouthfuls of that meal or a meal or two meals, as
he has prepared it."

